===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''McJob''' (''plural'' '''McJobs''')
#(''slang'') A job paying low wages, requiring few skills and having little opportunity for promotion.
#:''I got a '''McJob''' bus(s)ing tables at the local taco joint.''

====Etymology====
[[Mc]], from the name of the restaurant franchise [[w:McDonald's Corporation|McDonald's]] and [[job]], due to jobs at McDonald's having a reputation of consisting of menial tasks and with employees having little or no influence over their work situation.

